INSERT INTO public.equipment (eq_identity_name, eq_location, eq_identity, provider_id, ne_object_id, code)
SELECT
    eq_identity_name,
    eq_location,
    eq_identity,
    provider_id,
    ne_object_id,
    cs.code  
FROM
    public.equipment eq
JOIN
    public.cell_site cs ON eq.code = cs.code
WHERE
    cs.code IS NOT NULL
ON CONFLICT (eq_identity_name) DO NOTHING;

INSERT INTO network (ne_object_id, ne_type)
SELECT
    ne_object_identity,
    ne_type
FROM
    alarm_log_staging
ON CONFLICT (ne_object_id) DO NOTHING;

INSERT INTO public.equipment_alarm (equipment_id, alarm_id)
SELECT 
    object_identity_name AS equipment_id,
    CAST(alarm_id AS INTEGER) AS alarm_id
FROM 
    public.alarm_log_staging
WHERE 
    object_identity_name IS NOT NULL
    AND alarm_id IS NOT NULL
ON CONFLICT (equipment_id, alarm_id) DO NOTHING;

WITH unique_codes AS (
    SELECT
        CAST(alarm_id AS integer) AS alarm_id,
        alarm_name,
        type AS alarm_type,
        severity AS alarm_severity,
        log_serial_number,
        status AS alarm_status,
        occurrence_time AS alarm_occurrence_time,
        alarm_source,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY alarm_id ORDER BY alarm_id) AS row_num
    FROM public.alarm_log_staging
    WHERE alarm_id IS NOT NULL 
)
INSERT INTO public.alarm (alarm_id, alarm_name, alarm_type, alarm_severity, log_serial_number, alarm_status, alarm_occurrence_time, alarm_source)
SELECT
    alarm_id,
    alarm_name,
    alarm_type,
    alarm_severity,
    log_serial_number,
    alarm_status,
    alarm_occurrence_time,
    alarm_source
FROM unique_codes uc
WHERE row_num = 1 AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT alarm_id FROM public.alarm ar WHERE uc.alarm_id = ar.alarm_id);

INSERT INTO cell_site (cell_site_id, site_location, cell_name, code, longitude, altitude, sut_lot, start_date, end_date, update_dttm, technologie)
WITH unique_codes AS (
    SELECT
        cell_site_id,
        site_location,
        cell_name,
        code,
        CAST(REPLACE(longitude, ',', '.') AS text) AS longitude,
        CAST(REPLACE(altitude, ',', '.') AS text) AS altitude,
        CAST(sut_lot AS integer) AS sut_lot,
        CASE WHEN start_date ~ '^[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{4}$' THEN TO_DATE(start_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') ELSE NULL END AS start_date,
        CASE WHEN end_date ~ '^[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{4}$' THEN TO_DATE(end_date, 'DD/MM/YYYY') ELSE NULL END AS end_date,
        CASE WHEN update_dttm ~ '^[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{4}$' THEN TO_DATE(update_dttm, 'DD/MM/YYYY') ELSE NULL END AS update_dttm,
        technologie,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY code ORDER BY cell_site_id) AS row_num
    FROM cell_site_staging
    WHERE code IS NOT NULL AND end_date = '31/12/2999'
)
SELECT
    cell_site_id,
    site_location,
    cell_name,
    code,
    longitude,
    altitude,
    sut_lot,
    start_date,
    end_date,
    update_dttm,
    technologie
FROM unique_codes uc
WHERE row_num = 1
ON CONFLICT (code) DO NOTHING;

INSERT INTO region (commune, wilaya, region, code_commune, code_wilaya)
SELECT
    commune,
    wilaya,
    region,
    CAST(code_commune AS integer),
    CAST(code_wilaya AS integer)
FROM cell_site_staging
WHERE code_commune IS NOT NULL
ON CONFLICT (code_commune) DO NOTHING;
